_sText:
Gg_maniacal is a map with 3 main "corridors" or lines of fire. 2 side ones and a central "shooting range". There are lots of nooks to take cover in or camp in. 

The sides of the map also have a 2nd story. Snipers and "flankers" will learn to use this to their advantage.

Make a rush to the central bridge, and you'll find the one-way windows very helpful. You can see out but they cant see in!

Dont forget that the Terrorist and CounterTerrorist spawn-bunkers have oneway windows too. Especially when you have chosen the central lane.
